text: Ahmet Hüsamettin Cindoruk (born 1933) is a Turkish politician. He was the 17th Speaker of the Parliament of Turkey between 1991 to 1995. He was also the Acting President of Turkey in 1993 following the death of Turgut Özal.Biyografi.net - Biography of Hüsamettin Cindoruk ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Turkey Category:Speakers of the Parliament of Turkey Category:20th-century presidents of Turkey
